    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The issue here is that the condition that enables `GivesBounty` is not granted on actors that start as initial cargo.  `GrantConditionOnPrerequisite` seems to rely on the actor being added to the world in order to register for notifications, so it makes sense that this would not work - what isn't clear is why this worked at all in previous releases."
