    "body": "> what isn't clear is why this worked at all in previous releases.\r\n\r\nTurns out that this is actually broken even worse on `release-20180307` than on the current playtest: it only gives 40 credits, but the cash tick incorrectly shows 60.  The changes required to fix this are high risk, so I don't think we can justify delaying the release further for this seeing as it is not a new regression."
